This is a LES project template.  

Build your own LES project by running:

  $ svn export http://svn.unto.net/svn/public/les/trunk [PROJECT_NAME]


Edit [PROJECT_NAME]/Build.PL and add values for:
 
  $PROJECT_NAME   (e.g., 'delancey')
  $SITE_NAME      (e.g., 'unto.net')
  $PACKAGE        (e.g., 'Unto' )

Run:

  $ mkdir lib/[PACKAGE_NAME]
  $ mv lib/Les.pm lib/[PACKAGE_NAME]/[UC_PROJECT_NAME].pm

Edit lib/[PACKAGE_NAME]/[UC_PROJECT_NAME].pm and fill in the missing
information.

Start adding packages unde lib/[PACKAGE_NAME]/.  Add web service
calls to conf/configuration.yml.in.  Add files under htdocs, templates
under templates, etc.

Oh, and edit this file as well.
